author: stefan2
msg: Restrict the FSFS L2P index page size to powers of two.  That's easier
to verify and consistent with all the other settings we have.
(write_config): Update and clean up fsfs.conf docstring.
(get_l2p_header_body): Verify that the L2P page size is 2^N.

msg: QPID-6079 : [Java Broker] Objects created as duplicates should be automatically deleted

author: stefan2
msg: Harden FSFS f7 index reader against corruption.  The idea is to compare
header information to rev / pack file sizes etc. and error out when
they don't match.  This e.g. prevents OOM due to corrupt table sizes.
get_p2l_header): Add lots of data checking code.
